{"tid":1513486,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【中環在線】小米抽錯水 官媒鬧冇腦 - 李華華","createTime":"2019-08-28T10:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:47:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eba7622088235268cfa644ed6aa8bbb37efd3405","tid":1513486,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190828/20757502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F20757502&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=fdaf9255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190828%2F20757502&h=11cd3c22\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190828/20757502</a><br />\n<br />\n【中環在線】小米抽錯水 官媒鬧冇腦 - 李華華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190828/large/1566924056_8923.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190828%2Flarge%2F1566924056_8923.gif&h=e9fbb8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅米官方微博昨以「五大平台 缺一不可」作宣傳，隨即被官媒環球網發現及留言「缺腦如此、無藥可救」。<br />\n<br />\n小米（1810）網上抽水宣傳不嬲都好勁，但點知今次抽正「火水」，仲疑似激嬲阿爺！話說今年小米力谷家電市場，又出雪櫃又出冷氣機，嚟緊仲會出埋「紅米電視」，早前CFO周受資仲講到明，唔怕同差唔多時間出電視嘅華為對撼。<br />\n<br />\n面對「愛國代言人」華為，小米一啲都冇鬆懈，噚日喺紅米官方微博發圖，寫住「五大平台 缺一不可」用來宣傳五大電視App。但冇耐官媒環球網就發現，並留言「缺腦如此、無藥可救」。小米心知不秒，即刻將圖片刪除，並改成「海量內容」，環球網亦回覆指「知錯就改，加強學習」。有翻開牆嘅內地網民一睇就知點解，「米粉」就護航話「五星紅旗 缺一不可」；有人認為環球網過份敏感，表示「好大的官威啊！當代文字獄第一媒體。」雖然「抽錯水」，但張圖唔夠一日已經有過萬「like」，宣傳費都慳唔少。<br />\n<br />\n李華華<br />\nLiWaWa@AppleDaily.com <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLiWaWa@AppleDaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美銀美林看淡 人幣料年底見7.5<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n禹洲地產外幣債佔比高"},{"pid":"ff0ca7add6c6ddf3752109f0e9e647be09ebb074","tid":1513486,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前小米個FB個廣告抽得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247baf4d0983ad8e15a2baf3392bb283e2cfb3e3","tid":1513486,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"邊位手足做小米？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13917cda99c42b7bd89ac4352f1c11100d01de2f","tid":1513486,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"247baf4d0983ad8e15a2baf3392bb283e2cfb3e3","tid":1513486,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"邊位手足做小米？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭個仔(前員工)"},{"pid":"88017062cfd3d5b24e37ae4722ed53ba78017197","tid":1513486,"uid":155246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a7245edb5270634e6ba2a831ce468559d96f74","tid":1513486,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小米即刻升"},{"pid":"219065228566b1bdb453f7c50f12ee984c62496b","tid":1513486,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"小米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}